window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>One God Down. An Entire Pantheon To Go. Who's Next?</p> <p>Felix and his allies have saved Pax'Vrell and won the battle against the Pathless...but the war has only just begun. The Divine are stirring, and the Hierophant has her own deadly schemes.</p> <p>The fates of the Unbound rest on the choices Felix makes to protect them all. But as the gods close in, he begins to realize the terrible truth:</p> <p>If he fails, he risks more than their lives.</p> <p>He risks Ruin itself.</p>"; 
